"children":[
"Red Eye"
]
},
"children":[
{
"type":"p",
"hlId":"326c42",
"children":[
"Red eye consists of categories of entities with or without ocular pain and/or visual loss. ",
{
"type":"alert",
"children":[
"The combination of red eye, ocular pain, and visual loss warrants emergent referral to an ophthalmologist."
]
},
" Select Snellen visual acuity testing for all patients."
]
},
{
"type":"inline-wrap",
"wrapId":"1",
